object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct lr.lob_display_desc as lob_display_desc_pms, trim(pmp.policy_key) as policy_key_pms
FROM 
dbo.pms_master_policy pmp 
JOIN dbo.lob_ref lr
  ON pmp.lob_desc = lr.pms_lob_desc --

FROM
dbo.policydetail pd
JOIN dbo.lob_ref lr
  ON pd.lineofbusiness = lr.gw_lob_desc --
